{"title":"BEE IT","description":"\u003cp\u003eBEE IT, a fun word game full of meanings and connections: BE as being, BEE as bees, IT as what you want, what you are! But also as Made in Italy.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003eBEE IT wants to instill the message that every day we can be happy if we make the decision to BE! BEE IT!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eBeelieve in Yourself is their slogan because they believe that being treated makes you feel better. If we add environmental protection actions to this taken care of aspect, then we can face our daily life without limits and go back to believing in ourselves. To dream.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe Responsible Cosmetics means being and acting responsibly for the brand, for the environment, for bees.\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"bee-it-regenerating-shower-gel-250ml","title":"BEE IT Regenerating Shower Gel 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSensory body wash with naturally active biological ingredients with a regenerating action.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003ePromotes the natural feeling of well-being thanks to the beneficial properties of propolis and organic honey.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eApply all over the body. Rinse off, appreciating your moment.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eAqua [Water], Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Parfum [Fragrance], Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Potassium sorbate, Sodium benzoate, Citric acid, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Coumarin, Limonene, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354419503431,"sku":"","price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-regenerating-shower-gel-250ml-523322.jpg?v=1739897335"},{"product_id":"bee-it-nourishing-shampoo-250ml","title":"BEE IT Nourishing Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNourishing shampoo for damaged hair and scalp. It cleanses with care, maintaining the original structure of the hair with an energetic action. The soft creamy texture creates a light lather with extra ordinary effectiveness for soft and vital hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to wet scalp and hair, massaging gently. Rinse gently, inhaling and exhaling slowly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua [Water], Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Phenoxyethanol, Xanthan gum, Glycerin, Disodium cocoamphodiacetate, Parfum [Fragrance], Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Citric acid, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Panthenol, Argania spinosa kernel oil, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Mel\/Honey*, Coumarin, Limonene, Dehydroacetic acid, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, CI 19140 [Yellow 5].\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354464756039,"sku":null,"price":12.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-nourishing-shampoo-250ml-159598.jpg?v=1739897346"},{"product_id":"bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-250ml-1","title":"BEE IT Reconstruction Hair Mask 200ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA concentrated repairing post shampoo mask which gratifies for its immediate effectiveness. Gives strength and elasticity, deeply hydrating and nourishing for a healthy, luminous and plumped up hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply after shampooing to towel-dried hair. Leave on for 5-10 minutes, then comb and rinse. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Behenamidopropyl dimethylamine, Cetearyl alcohol, Lactic acid, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Tocopheryl acetate, Sorbitol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea fruit oil*, Opuntia ficus-indica seed oil, Glycerin, Myrtus communis extract, Panthenol, Hamamelis virginiana leaf extract*, Mel*, Propolis, Retinyl palmitate, Limonene, Linalool, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354507583815,"sku":null,"price":14.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-200ml-244590.jpg?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-250ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Blue for Kids 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class