c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to face\/body after sun exposure, ready for the wow effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua [Water], Polysorbate 20, Parfum [Fragrance], Carbomer, Mannitol, Phenoxyethanol, Microcrystalline cellulose, Sodium hydroxide, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Ethylhexylglycerin, Propanediol, CI 77492 [Iron oxides], CI 77491 [Iron oxides], Mica, Acmella oleracea extract, Acrylates\/ammonium methacrylate copolymer, CI 77891 [Titanium dioxide], Tocopheryl acetate, Triethyl citrate, Caprylic\/capric triglyceride, CI 77499 [Iron oxides], Titanium dioxide, Hydroxypropyl methylcellulose, Sodium hyaluronate, 1,2-Hexanediol, Simethicone, Inositol, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT",