sis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138338058567,"sku":null,"price":4.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-regenerating-shower-gel-250ml-523322.jpg?v=1739897335"},{"product_id":"bee-it-nourishing-shampoo-50ml","title":"BEE IT Nourishing Shampoo 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNourishing shampoo for damaged hair and scalp. It cleanses with care, maintaining the original structure of the hair with an energetic action. The soft creamy texture creates a light lather with extra ordinary effectiveness for soft and vital hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply to wet scalp and hair, massaging gently. Rinse gently, inhaling and exhaling slowly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua [Water], Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Phenoxyethanol, Xanthan gum, Glycerin, Disodium cocoamphodiacetate, Parfum [Fragrance], Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Citric acid, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Panthenol, Argania spinosa kernel oil, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Mel\/Honey*, Coumarin, Limonene, Dehydroacetic acid, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, CI 19140 [Yellow 5].\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138350772551,"sku":null,"price":4.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-nourishing-shampoo-250ml-159598.jpg?v=1739897346"},{"product_id":"bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-50ml","title":"BEE IT Reconstruction Hair Mask 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA concentrated repairing post shampoo mask which gratifies for its immediate effectiveness. Gives strength and elasticity, deeply hydrating and nourishing for a healthy, luminous and plumped up hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply after shampooing to towel-dried hair. Leave on for 5-10 minutes, then comb and rinse. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Behenamidopropyl dimethylamine, Cetearyl alcohol, Lactic acid, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Tocopheryl acetate, Sorbitol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea fruit oil*, Opuntia ficus-indica seed oil, Glycerin, Myrtus communis extract, Panthenol, Hamamelis virginiana leaf extract*, Mel*, Propolis, Retinyl palmitate, Limonene, Linalool, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138364764487,"sku":null,"price":4.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\