789"},{"product_id":"bee-it-sun-spf50-maya-50ml","title":"BEE IT SUN SPF50 Maya 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eHigh protection sun milk, effective and protecting the skin from both UVA and UVB rays. Suitable for sensitive skin and also suitable for kids under 3 years old. Protects skin against aging, sun spots and keeps skin hydrated.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAlso effective in protecting the bees!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to face\/body before sun exposure until absorbed. Repeat the application frequently for a safe, even and long-lasting tan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua [Water], Ethylhexyl methoxycinnamate, Octocrylene, Butyl methoxydibenzoylmethane, Methylene bis-benzotriazolyl tetramethylbutylphenol, Helianthus annuus (Sunflower) seed oil, Glyceryl stearate SE, Prunus amygdalus dulcis (Sweet almond) oil, Glycerin, Phenoxyethanol, Decyl glucoside, Tocopheryl acetate, Citric acid, Parfum [Fragrance], Ethylhexylglycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea (Olive) fruit oil*, Oryza sativa (Rice) bran oil, Vitis vinifera (Grape) seed oil, Allantoin, Propylene glycol, Xanthan gum, Vaccinium myrtillus (Myrtle) fruit extract, Avena sativa (Oat) kernel extract*, Calendula officinalis flower extract*, Sodium hydroxide, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52143723315527,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-sun-spf50-maya-50ml-7388105.png?v=1756222789"},{"product_id":"bee-it-hand-and-body-cream-50ml","title":"BEE IT Hand and Body Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMoisturizing hand and body cream, soft and scented, exquisite for dry, reddened and in need of attention skin. Enriched with oils, vitamins, propoli and organic honey, it nourishes your skin making it supple, radiant and fragrant. Soft and light like a caress, it removes daily stress and promotes a pleasant feeling of relaxation in every part of your body and mind.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Use every day after a shower or bath on dry skin. Apply all over the body and massage gently until completely absorbed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Glyceryl stearate SE, Cetearyl alcohol, Ethylhexyl palmitate, Parfum, Glycerin, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Potassium sorbate, Sodium benzoate, Citric acid, Tocopheryl acetate, Mel*, Propolis, Coumarin, Limonene, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Linalool, Geraniol, Isoeugenol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52245324169543,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-hand-and-body-cream-50ml-5351249.png?v=1756636043"},{"product_id":"bee-it-face-cream-50ml","title":"BEE IT Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMoisturizing and anti-age prevention face cream, with a soft and light texture, easy to apply. It has professional efficacy with 100% natural origin active ingredients NaturOxygen® and Pentavitin® EcoCert, Cosmos and Natrue certified, which increase metabolism and skin turnover, making the skin nourished, radiant and even younger. Enriched with Sodium Hyaluronate, Shea butter, Vitamin E, propolis and organic honey.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply and massage with circular movements to regenerate the skin, releasing your emotions.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Helianthus annuus (Sunflower) seed oil, Cetearyl alcohol, Prunus amygdalus dulcis (Sweet almond) oil, Ethylhexyl palmitate, Cetearyl glucoside, Sorbitan olivate, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum [Fragrance], Butyrospermum parkii (Shea) butter, Glycerin, Cyamopsis tetragonoloba (guar) gum, Tocopheryl acetate, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Citric acid, Coumarin, Limonene, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Saccharide isomerate, Hydroxycitronellal, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax, Saccharomyces lysate, Disodium succinate, Sodium citrate, Glutamic acid, Glycine, Threonine, Valine.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52245337014599,"sku":null,"price":10.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-face-cream-50ml-9846172.png?v=1756636044"}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/collections\/bee-it-113597.jpg?v=1739979820","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/bee-it.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}